"diplomatically nod and welcome them aboard."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:592
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_GOODEND_RK_FIREGHOST\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "I think they'll fit right in."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:598
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_LOSTSUN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"They bring you the slave and remove his restraints so quickly that you haven't even transferred all the scrap yet. Unfortunately the troublemaker doesn't seem to like the way some of your crew look at him, and starts punching! \n"
"\tYou interrupt the scrap transfer and watch the slavers immediately jump away, leaving you to deal with him."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:607
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_LOSTSUN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "So that's why he was so cheap."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:612
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_DUSKBRINGER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"They bring you the slave and remove his restraints so quickly that you haven't even transferred all the scrap yet. Unfortunately the troublemaker doesn't seem to like the way some of your crew look at him, and starts punching! \n"
"\tYou interrupt the scrap transfer and watch the slavers immediately jump away, leaving you to deal with him."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:621
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_ENSLAVED_BADEND_DUSKBRINGER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "So that's why he was so cheap."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:626
msgid ""
