msgstr "So that's why he was so cheap."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:681
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/text"
msgstr "You notice a Theocracy ship nearby, they immediately hail you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:685
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Take the hail."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:687
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Greetings, pagan. We buy RadiKal weapons, and we believe you have some. We"
" pay even more than their usual buy price.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:690
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "\"Is that so?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:692
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:695
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "\"...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:697
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"... ...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:700
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "\"... ... ...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:702
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You realize they are not going to elaborate, and start considering it. What "
"do you decide?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:706
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Bada beam for 165~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:708
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future. They leave without a word."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:716
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_1\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Heavy Popper MK I laser for 90~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:718
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future. They leave without a word."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:726
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_2\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Heavy Popper MK II laser for 120~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:728
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"RK_HEAVY_POPPER_2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
