#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:863
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_commando\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Commando Crew) \"That kind of gear is not for brainwashed asshats. You "
"should have stayed in your neighbourhood of stagnation and lies.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:865
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_commando\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship's captain suddenly regains the ability for speech. \"Hah! I see you"
" work with terrorists. Once again, my brothers, witness how egotistic and "
"violent the heretics are. Let us punish them!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:868
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"rock_commando\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:875
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[17]/text"
msgstr "Decline."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:877
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[17]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You think about the profit you could have made from this encounter, but also remember that selling your weapons to random passerbys isn't a very safe strategy.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou still have time to do something around the ship instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:882
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[17]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:886
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[17]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:902
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:904
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You don't know what they want, but do know you aren't interested in the "
"Theocracy's deals right now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:906
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:910
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ROCKMAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:919
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Another ship, seemingly foreign, arrives at the beacon shortly after you do,"
" looking uneasy. You could hail them and ask what's going on."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:922
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hail them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:924
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Hello, military ship. Um... You don't look like a RadiKal\"."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:927
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Neither do you. What does it matter?."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:929
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The ship's captain hesitates a brief moment. \"You see, we are here on an... armament surveying mission you could say. And we need samples of RK gear.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tYou make a mental note that this must be a secret mission, as the Ministry wouldn't normally be caught dead buying illegal weaponry."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:932
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Well why don't you go and get those samples?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:934
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you look trustworthy enough to that captain, because he finally spills the beans. \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"The people in that sector don't have the best reputation and it would be regrettable for us to be seen doing business with them. We were also not really provided the right equipment to take it by force from them and then leave alive...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask them why they're telling you this."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:939
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Well if you have any, sell us some. We even pay more than you probably "
"bought them for. Please?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:943
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Bada beam for 165~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:945
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
