"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"RK_FOCUS_FIRE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future. They leave without a word."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1078
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your Rain of Fire launcher for 120~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1080
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1089
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/text"
msgstr "Sell them your BPS Messenger laser for 200~."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1091
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You try to hide your satisfaction while they transfer the excessive payment,"
" but also hope some unfortunate encounter won't make you regret the sale in "
"the near future."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1100
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[16]/text"
msgstr "Decline."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1102
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[16]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You think about the profit you could have made from this encounter, but also remember that selling your weapons to random passerbys isn't a very safe strategy.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou still have time to do something around the ship instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1107
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[16]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1111
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[16]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1120
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(RadiKal gear) Power up your weapons before they take YOUR equipment by "
"force."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1122
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Alright alright, no need to resort to violence. We'll be on our way.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1125
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"...Well that means they're as weak as they said, let's make some easy scrap!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1127
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Wait... Wait! Thi-this was just a trade request. How did it come to this? Please!\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAs you suspected from the covert nature of their mission, they're not sending any message to denounce you, merely firing up their engines to escape! Looks like you've found a place where crime can go unpunished..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1131
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1138
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave them be, they are clearly no threat."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1149
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SHIP\"]/text"
msgstr "That's funny. How did you get here without ever seeing an RK ship?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1151
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SHIP\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"What? Wait how would you know that?.. Oh I see, this must in fact be a "
"RadiKal ship! Can we... have it? We will compensate you greatly."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1154
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SHIP\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Hmmmmm, no."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1156
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SHIP\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Figured as much... but understand that my whole family died to a RadiKal raid while I was on duty. I didn't take this assignment at random. We need access to hinder their operations, and I really can't let that opportunity pass. I wish you had cooperated, it pains me to do this but I must!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTheir weapons are coming online!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1162
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_SHIP\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1173
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1175
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You leave them to whatever troubles they're having, and think about doing "
"some maintenance on your ship instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1177
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1181
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1199
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans escape before you can slaughter them for scrap, and contrary to "
"what you thought, actually do denounce you. Fair enough."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1201
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1212
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a welcoming, lively senior hermit in a small space station chock-full of civilian and military supplies, apparently all for herself. \n"
"\t\t\"Hello foreigner, I know all about this sector, care to listen and have some tea?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1215
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Stay for a while. This could be helpful."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1217
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Name's Bruntilda. As you've certainly noticed, this sector is occupied by "
"three main subfactions, and they all have their own personality!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1219
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Politely interrupt and ask where those supplies came from."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1221
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, aren't you curious! You see my dear, my sons work in this sector in "
"\"management\" and \"marketing\" positions. At one point they realized they "
"didn't have the time or patience to assess newcomers and teach them our "
"ways. So they came up with this gig for their sweet ol' mama, and they're "
"always making sure I am cared for.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1223
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "I see. Nice to meet you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1225
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that you can guess why nobody's pillaged the place yet, there are things"
" you could learn about. \"What else would you like to know, dear?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1227
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Think of some questions."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1238
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We don't have time to waste with some grandma's \"intel\"."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1240
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You say goodbye, gaining and losing nothing, which isn't that bad when you "
"think about it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1243
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1247
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1260
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr "Ask her..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1263
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "... about the Gatekeepers."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1265
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"This is supposed to be a bit of a surprise, but I've met some charming lads and lassies who never made it out of the sector because they didn't know. So I'll tell you: you're not leaving the sector without a fight (unless you're transporting one of our friends, hah!). Steer clear until you're prepared.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Bam gatekeeper will be a tough nut to crack, but any missile defense and sufficient shielding should keep you safe.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Punk gatekeeper has a bit of a chaotic mess going on, but it's mostly ion and anti-bio damage you must watch out for.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Scorch gatekeeper will have you on fire soon and repeatedly, and that won't work too well against it either. But surely you already figured that one out!\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tJust don't let my sons know I told you all that, Heeeheeehee! Oh and you can always just run away if you're a pussycat...\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can tell that even she would no longer respect you if you did that, but you must also think about the reality you're trying to save."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1278
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1282
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1284
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1286
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1294
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "... about the subfaction names."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1296
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"What kind of names are those? RadiKal Bam? Punk? Scorch? Is it from a kid's show or something?\" you ask.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Not much to it really. Since so many people have been calling them radicals from the beginning of this little operation, my sons and their little friends simply embraced it. The subfactions just needed a little extra to tell themselves apart, and people don't really like talking too much around here. So they kept it short and to the point. Also I've heard something about variables? I'm the exception, chatting is so enjoyable!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1302
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1306
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1308
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1310
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1318
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "... about the RK equipment design philosophy."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1320
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Maybe you're just a little slow in the head, so just in case, let me lay it out for youuu.\" You repress the urge to respond to the insult.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Members of Bam believe in the blunt efficiency of impactful, stunning hits or events. Such as a good bonk to the dome, like I taught my children!\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe Punk prefer technological superiority, counter-intelligence and all that jazz. They tend to bring less firepower and more fancy gadgets to the table.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tLastly the Scorch just want to watch things burn, and have ways to make sure they do. Some jealous foreigners like to spout nonsense about pacts with otherwordly creatures, especially among the Scorch. Isn't it sad, how low people will go?\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tI hope that clears it up for y'all youngsters!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1331
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1335
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1337
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1339
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1347
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "... about the prices."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1349
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"It takes a lot of specialized equipment to discreetly get so many crafting"
" materials into a hidden sector, or so my sons told me. That leads to high "
"prices, but not so much for the local production of course!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1352
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1356
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1358
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1360
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1391
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Threaten her for the supplies!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1393
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Emboldened by her physical frailty, you decide chatting is never gonna be as"
" useful as just taking what you want."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1395
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "How about you just shut up and give us all of those suppl-"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1397
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can finish your despicable threat, you feel the cold dagger belonging to a cloaked security drone pressing on your neck, and realize this whole place is obviously heavily defended.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Uneducated scallywags, eh? Another disappointment, but it is clear that our little business is attractive to this type of people. What a waste of good tea. Out with you now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1401
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Wait a sec! You won't believe it but, this really isn't who we are..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1403
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You shamefully \"offer\" some supplies as an apology, find out why the pile is so big, and tell your crew in very clear terms that this event is not to be talked about ever again.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou also feel like even though this happened in this hidden sector, word of your lack of morals could somehow reach the outside world."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1421
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1426
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"She looks cheerful. \"Why, thank you! Very few of you young'uns take a pause to listen to an old lady around these parts. For some reason they seem to favor... 'enhanced interrogation' I think the kids call it? Something about manufacturing details. Anyhoo, farewell!\"\n"
"\tYou notice a shuttle sent to share a little of her supplies with you. That job might be lonelier than it looks, and you wonder how often her sons visit her."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1432
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1445
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you get here, you notice that you're surrounded by a small Zoltan fleet intercepting every ship passing through here. An urgent hail from a heavily armed Zoltan Elite comes through. \n"
"\t\tNeedless to say, it would look suspicious not to take the hail."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1453
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Answer it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1455
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"As you may know if you're not a brainless savage, this sector has been providing armament to the Duskbringers. We have recently started tackling this problem.\n"
"\t\t\t\tLike any vessel in transit in a lawless armament-manufacturing area like this one, you will be subjected to the mandatory thorough search for said armament. The fight against illegal weapon proliferation starts with you. Do not resist.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Zoltan Ministry considers this area a very serious issue. If they find any RadiKal equipment a fine must be paid, based on how many you're carrying."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1462
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/text"
msgstr "(Zoltan Peacekeeper) We were sent to help you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1464
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"At last, the reinforcements. Here is your warrant. You'll find criminals in this sector, usually hiding in hazardous beacons. Seize their illegal gear and drop it off at the station. The coordinates are on the back.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tIt's safe to assume that not every \"criminal\" will relinquish their RK gear without a fight, but this could greatly benefit your mission."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1471
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1475
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1482
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/text"
msgstr "(Human Soldier) We were sent to help you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1484
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"At last, the reinforcements. Here is your warrant. You'll find criminals in this sector, usually hiding in hazardous beacons. Seize their illegal gear and drop it off at the station. The coordinates are on the back.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tIt's safe to assume that not every \"criminal\" will relinquish their RK gear without a fight, but this could greatly benefit your mission."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1491
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1495
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1502
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1507
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Ask what happens if you refuse."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1509
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Thanks to the merciful recent amendment 3473-B delta, captains may choose to participate in the funding of control vessels like this one, and report to the closest Zoltan police station within 72 cycles instead of immediately submitting to the search.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tEven though you have no intention of taking that detour, they would leave you alone for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1514
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pay up."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1516
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You begrudgingly transfer the scrap but manage to not look mad about it, "
"taking comfort in the fact that your equipment's safe... at least for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1524
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1533
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Try to ignore it and just pass through."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1535
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You admission of guilt in facilitating terrorist operations has been recorded and filed for the trial of any surviving spouse(s) and/or heir(s). You will not escape the law.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tSounds like you'll have to fight your way through. You wonder whether having an insider in your crew could have changed this outcome."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1541
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1564
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/text"
msgstr "They come aboard and search your ship..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1567
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1569
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Luckily you had nothing to worry about, and after leaving your ship, without"
" a word the Zoltans immediately cut comms to focus on a different ship. You "
"wonder what could have happened. In any case this took a while, too long to "
"do anything special on your ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1571
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1578
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1580
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before long, they do find something. \"Understand that without justification"
" for this, which you may still provide, we will apply the necessary "
"sanctions, which may be a fine or outright confiscation of the offending "
"equipment. Both may be avoided if you willingly leave someone with us for "
"interrogation.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1582
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1590
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you forgot you were carrying RadiKal gear, or maybe you just didn't "
"find a way to avoid the search. Regardless, they are now fining you for each"
" piece!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1592
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1594
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"One illegal piece of gear, take this minimal fine as a warning. If you had"
" any more \"RadiKal\" gear than that, we would have been forced to direct "
"you to the local Police Station for processing.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1604
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1606
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Two illegal pieces of gear. You should really know better than to give up ethics for power.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1617
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1619
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Three illegal pieces of gear... The federation really hires any random scum these days.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1631
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1633
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_EQUIPMENT\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"AT LEAST FOUR illegal pieces of gear! What th-... I do not even wish to know. What a horrible person you must be. Luckily for you, this is the maximum fine stipulated in the applicable regulation. I suppose nobody foresaw that anyone would make themselves any more of a wretched menace to society than that.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1645
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CHECK_ANY_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr "Give someone up for interrogation instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1650
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Surprise headshot that nosy lightbulb. (Risky)"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1652
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Quickly but accurately aiming through the hardlight, you splatter the chief inspector with your blaster, right before taking cover for the explosion! \n"
"\t\t\tVery satisfying ... but can you deal with the rest of them?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1658
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Pop them all!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1666
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You come to an agreement where they keep one of your crew in custody so they"
" can explain what you were doing in this sector. It's a lengthy process, you"
" will certainly finish your mission (or die) before you see them again."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1669
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew cannot be cloned as they are not dead, though they might go insane"
" shortly."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1673
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1691
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "Where Zoltan Police holds confiscated RadiKal gear."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1693
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You wonder how exactly the Zoltans set up a fortified police station in such an area undeterred, but it is proof of their determination.\n"
"\t\t\"Welcome captain. Since you found this place, you must be part of the special Federation corps attached to this regulation effort.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tMight be far from the truth, but you decide to roll with it.\n"
"\t\t\"What can we do for you?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1702
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Request supplies."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1704
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We have seized quite a lot of supplies from this band of criminals, at "
"great cost. But as Federation you are our ally in this operation. Help "
"yourself, within the limits of the Alliance Supply and Logistics Act of "
"course.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1710
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Request RadiKal gear."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1712
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"After some brief icebreaker chitchat which the officer almost seems to enjoy, you take your shot asking for a free piece. What passes for his facial expression changes that instant.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Surely you must be confused. This is labeled and sorted trial evidence, in the form of illegal weaponry which is unsafe for use, unethical and generally a threat to law and order. Thanks for stopping by, I have work to do now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1717
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Feign surprise."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1719
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You expected this. \"Oh? We weren't informed. Sorry for asking, keep up the good work.\" \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Zoltan throws you a suspicious look, but he's too busy dealing with the paperwork to investigate. You're out without a hitch but with nothing to show for it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1724
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Meh."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1731
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "\"We can do this the hard way instead...\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1733
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now certain that you're not, in fact, here to help at all, the Zoltan rings "
"the alarm and you rush back to your ship. The fight is breaking out within "
"range of the station's defense turrets!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1744
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The police station breaks apart, its confiscated illegal contents and "
"extensive array of administrative backups reduced to mere scrap for you to "
"take."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1748
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Having killed the crew, you manage to snatch some supplies and a labeled "
"crate before the turrets tear your ship apart."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1751
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Open it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1753
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As the label suggested, it's a RadiKal augment! Bureaucracy has its "
"benefits."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1778
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears a heavily damaged laser-wielding RadiKal ship is under attack by "
"an Argeonn smuggler, certainly to steal their special tech. They are on "
"their last legs but their trajectory forces them to pass you by for a slim "
"chance at escaping."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1782
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Rescue the RadiKals."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1784
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You give the smuggler ship no choice but to fight you as you take position "
"in their way."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1787
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1794
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/text"
msgstr "(Upg. Weapons) Claim the prey for yourself."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1796
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Woh hoh hoh, hey, wait, that's our-\" They quickly change their mind as "
"the rest of the crew pressures them. \"You know what, screw this, have fun "
"with you ill-gotten goods.\" Quite ironic, coming from a smuggler. The "
"surviving RadiKals are easily dealt with."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1800
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Search the ship a little more."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1802
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"There was a functional RadiKal augment in the cargo! Must be what the "
"smugglers were after."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1806
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "I guess we're the thieves now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1817
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Stay back and watch how this unfolds."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1819
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal ship puts up a decent but hopeless fight and soon stops showing "
"signs of life. The pirates briefly do whatever they went in there for, then "
"re-open comms with you. \"Thank you for not interfering my good sir. Imagine"
" how much easier business would be if we had more cowa- I mean nice "
"bystanders like you around? Here's some fuel for your exemplary behavior, "
"and we're off to celebrate!\" You scoop up the reward and briefly wonder "
"what could have put them in such a good mood."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1827
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1834
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1836
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "You leave the ships to their fight and think about what to do next."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1839
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1843
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1863
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIP_SMUGGLER_RK_LASERS_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Accept their surrender."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1869
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SHIP_SMUGGLER_RK_LASERS_SURRENDER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Go and check on their would-be prey."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1880
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_REWARD\"]/text"
msgstr "\"Without you we were toast. Have this as thanks.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1884
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_REWARD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "What did they want from you?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1889
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_REWARD_CREWKILL\"]/text"
msgstr "\"Without you we were toast. Have this as thanks.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1893
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_REWARD_CREWKILL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "What did they want from you?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1899
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The usual, local tech. Surely you understand that we can't just give it to you either.\"\n"
"\t\tA voice in the back of your head tells you that you should have killed them then... but you keep your greed in check and dismiss the intrusive thoughts.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\"However we can provide you one non-RadiKal laser weapon that fits the style of an RK subfaction, that would only be fair. Which one is it?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1906
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Bam"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1908
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "They transfer the weapon and wish you safe travels."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1911
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1918
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Punk"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1920
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_LASERS_END\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "They transfer the weapon and wish you safe travels."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1923
msgid ""
