msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1946
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears a damaged missile-wielding RadiKal ship is under attack by a "
"smuggler, certainly to steal their special tech. They are on their last legs"
" but their trajectory forces them to pass you by for a slim chance at "
"escaping."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1950
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Rescue the RadiKals."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1952
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You give the smuggler ship no choice but to fight you as you fly towards it "
"full speed."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1955
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1962
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/text"
msgstr "(Upg. Weapons) Claim the prey for yourself."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1964
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Woh hoh hoh, hey, wait, that's our-\" They quickly change their mind as "
"the rest of the crew pressures them. \"You know what, screw this, have fun "
"with you ill-gotten goods.\" Quite ironic, coming from a smuggler. The "
"Radikals are quickly dealt with."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1968
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Search the ship a little more."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1970
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[@req=\"weapons\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"There was a functional RadiKal augment in the cargo! Must be what the "
"smugglers were after. Looks like you're the thief now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1978
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Ignore them."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1980
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal ship soon stops moving, and the pirates re-open comms to thank "
"you for not interfering, toss you a scrap bag through an airlock, and jump "
"away. You briefly wonder what could have put them in such a good mood."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1986
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"THIEVES_RK_MISSILES\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

